text: (a iddaru strilato ila anabadindi): "Okavela miriddaru allah vaipunaku pascattapanto maralite (adi mi meluke) vastavaniki mi iddari hrdayalu (rjumargam nundi) tolagipoyayi. Okavela miriddaru pravaktaku virodhanga pote! Niscayanga, allah atani sanraksakudu mariyu jibril mariyu satpurusulaina visvasulu atani (sahayakulu). Mariyu devadutalandaru kuda atani sahayakulani (telusukondi)
